Bonzii is a free pocket pet for your iPhone or iPod Touch. Think you can collect & grow them all? Download it on iTunes today!
Every Bonziis has three unique stages of evolution. Keep your Bonzii alive long enough and see what they look like all grown up.
Bonziis love to nom. That's why there are over 40 different eats for all their weird taste buds.
Your bonziis won't stay happy if they're all dirty, smelly & have weird things growing on them. Keep 'em squeeky clean so they  live long & happy lives.
Play super cool mini-games like NOMINATOR to win Kiwii koins to buy awesome in-game items and food!
You can find, grow, & collect all types of Bonziis, and If you're skilled enough, you might just find the real  rare ones.